          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1692348246049-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fresh orecchiette</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the orecchiette for 4-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the orecchiette, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1692348249250-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1692348249250-x400.jpg",
