          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1692348252743-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened and the sausage meat is cooked through (no pink meat!), stir in the<strong> fresh orecchiette </strong>with <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> sausage, leek & fennel sauce with fresh orecchiette</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
